# Main body/case (dark wood)
rect 0.12,0.12 2.76,2.76 texfill polyhaven/dark_wood 0.85
rect 0.12,0.12 2.76,2.76 stroke #2a1400
# Keyboard strip (front/south edge, seen from above)
